{"id": "1195408669018427513", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "1187994440019746886", "author_name": "kkklavier", "author_bot": false, "content": "有人可以解析一下環形拉蒙嗎😭😭 負熵的功能是什麼啊（我的技能頁面不知道為啥下面的解釋被切掉xDDD）\n配原本的夫人隊可行嗎？還是有什麼其他適合的配法～", "timestamp": "2024-01-12T16:47:16.313000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1195414555514380338", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "724055506817253436", "author_name": "angrytone", "author_bot": false, "content": "負熵有兩個獲取方法\n1-靈芝覺醒環拉\n2-環拉一啟後，每回合結束獲得一層\n疊滿三層後，下一張打出的環拉的卡牌就會被賦予額外效果，", "timestamp": "2024-01-12T17:10:39.763000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1195414856296304640", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "724055506817253436", "author_name": "angrytone", "author_bot": false, "content": "目前的2費-從抽牌堆裡拉牌的效果算是比較值得注意。\n三費劍沒什麼好說的，該賣就賣", "timestamp": "2024-01-12T17:11:51.475000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1195415458631913564", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "724055506817253436", "author_name": "angrytone", "author_bot": false, "content": "大招還在鑽研中，但如果是夫人隊的話，我會覺得原本的拉就很好用了\n原本的大招沒有限制，開了就能拿牌\n但環拉的大招會限制你的出牌順序，2費卡也是只能拉抽牌堆", "timestamp": "2024-01-12T17:14:15.083000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙏🏻", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1195416091841810554", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "724055506817253436", "author_name": "angrytone", "author_bot": false, "content": "再來也不能變出「複數的相同卡」和「衍生卡」，那這樣配合上就會變得非常嚴峻", "timestamp": "2024-01-12T17:16:46.052000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
